        "inactive": true
      },
      "date": "2013-01-17 13:12:19.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nChris,\n\nYes, I know the lbuild.old_school file was removed already.  The problem is that lbuild is still trying to source it.  That is what needs to be removed.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
